<h6 id="sbb-itb-5a54c13" tabindex="-1">sbb-itb-5a54c13</h6>
<h2 id="6-multi-payment-processing-system" tabindex="-1">6. Multi-Payment Processing System</h2>
<p>In today’s fast-paced dining scene, offering flexible payment options isn’t just a nice-to-have - it’s a must. Research shows that <strong>73% of diners prefer using credit or debit cards</strong> when eating out <a href="https://www.touchbistro.com/blog/the-ultimate-guide-to-payment-processing-for-restaurants" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"><sup>[30]</sup></a>, and nearly <strong>50% of customers choose businesses that offer contactless payments</strong> <a href="https://www.heartland.us/resources/blog/everything-you-need-to-know-about-credit-card-processing-for-restaurants" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"><sup>[31]</sup></a>. Meeting these expectations can make or break a restaurant’s success.</p>
<h3 id="essential-payment-methods" tabindex="-1">Essential Payment Methods</h3>
<p>Modern diners expect a variety of payment choices, and each option brings its own benefits for both customers and businesses:</p>
