<h3 id="security-and-compliance" tabindex="-1">Security and Compliance</h3>
<p>With data breaches in the U.S. costing an average of <strong>$9.44 million</strong> <a href="https://stripe.com/en-cy/resources/more/payment-security" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"><sup>[36]</sup></a>, ensuring payment security is non-negotiable. A reliable POS system should include:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>End-to-end encryption</strong> to safeguard transactions.</li>
<li><strong>PCI DSS compliance</strong> to meet industry security standards.</li>
<li><strong>Real-time fraud detection</strong> to minimize risks.</li>
<li><strong>Tokenization technology</strong> to securely store payment data.</li>
</ul>
<p>These features not only protect customer information but also build trust, which keeps diners coming back.</p>
<h3 id="streamlined-operations" tabindex="-1">Streamlined Operations</h3>
<p>Integrated payment systems simplify restaurant workflows by connecting online and in-person orders seamlessly. This integration enhances efficiency across the board <a href="https://www.business.com/articles/restaurant-payment-processing" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"><sup>[33]</sup></a>.</p>
<h3 id="business-benefits" tabindex="-1">Business Benefits</h3>
<p>Adopting a robust payment system isn’t just about convenience - it’s about results. Consider these stats:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>73% of diners</strong> say restaurant technology improves their experience <a href="https://www.pateno.com/tip-disbursement/why-restaurants-need-multiple-payment-solutions" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"><sup>[34]</sup></a>.</li>
<li><strong>95% of restaurateurs</strong> report greater operational efficiency <a href="https://www.pateno.com/tip-disbursement/why-restaurants-need-multiple-payment-solutions" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"><sup>[34]</sup></a>.</li>
<li>Limited payment options lead to <strong>11% of customers abandoning their carts</strong> <a href="https://monei.com/blog/multiple-payment-options" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"><sup>[35]</sup></a>.</li>
</ul>
